video.title: Newly Rich, Newly Poor
video.synopsis: After learning they were switched at birth, wealthy Andrés and working-class Brayan must adjust to the parents and lifestyles they were meant to have.

episodes.synopsis: In a twist of fate, a tipsy hospital nurse makes an error that has far-reaching consequences for two baby boys born on the same day.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery helps Brayan find a new job, but has a rough first day as Andrés' secretary. Antonia investigates Lucero Molina and travels to Colombia.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Lucero fully confesses to Antonia. Andrés begins to show some interest in Rosmery. A flat tire brings Brayan face to face with his celebrity crush.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Desperate for rent money, Leonidas visits a loan shark. Redex agrees to a deal with Andrés — on one condition. Brayan makes a scene at work.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery makes an appeal to Andrés. Antonia and Leonidas launch a plan to force their sons to see the error of their ways. Mateo receives a shady offer.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Lucero arrives at the New Year's Eve dinner party, where she reveals all to Brayan and Andrés, who learn that their surnames — and lives — have changed.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: Andrés discovers the challenges of having no credit cards or cellphone. Meanwhile, Brayan is introduced to the wealthy lifestyle he's just inherited.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Andrés seeks help from Fernanda and Mateo. Brayan invites his friends to his new home, where his mother asks when he's planning to marry Rosmery.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: With nowhere else to turn, Andrés goes to stay with his father at Hostel La Caridad. Brayan is prepped for his first day of work as Express World's CEO.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: Brayan is introduced to the employees at Express World, while Andrés finds a way to sneak past security. Leonidas discovers that his cash stash is gone.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Brayan makes a splash at the country club, where Fernanda reluctantly makes her first move on him. Mateo is revisited by the whiskey smuggler.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: Miller confesses his feelings for Ingrid to her brother. Brayan tries to smooth things over with Rosmery. Andrés learns more about Rosmery from Maritza.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Antonia arranges a press conference for Brayan. Leonidas asks Brayan for a loan. Andrés meets a kindred spirit, who gives him some sage advice.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: Leonidas visits Antonia with a business proposal. Brayan and Rosmery face Redex in a videoconference. Andrés extends an offer to Brayan.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda tries to convince Brayan to go as her date to a high-society party. Leonidas interviews with Orlando for a job at the country club.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: Brayan and Fernanda arrive at the party. Fidel makes his first night delivery. The loan shark sends his goons to punish Leonidas for missing a payment.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Brayan is caught off guard at the party. Fidel is stopped at a police checkpoint. When Rosmery gets drunk at a cantina, Andrés must help her get home.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: The next morning, Rosmery recalls when she first met Brayan. Meanwhile, Brayan remembers happier times with Rosmery. Footage from the party airs on TV.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Antonia meets with Fernanda and asks what her intentions are. Ingrid figures out how Miller paid for his motorcycle. Andrés visits the loan shark.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Andrés struggles to get to his job interviews, so Rosmery accompanies him. Brayan insists that Ingrid help him shop for an engagement ring.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: Andrés invites Rosmery to spend more time with him. Brayan tries to win back Rosmery with a grand gesture. Mateo targets another woman to manipulate.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery begs Brayan to help Andrés find a job. Leonidas asks Andrés an uncomfortable question. Miller tries to woo a heartbroken Ingrid.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Andrés admits to Brayan that he not only needs a job, but also an advance. Leonidas starts his new job as a waiter at the country club.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Julio sets out to make Andrés miserable in his new job. Mateo tries to give Brayan second thoughts about marrying Rosmery. Leonidas attracts an admirer.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: On the job, Andrés is pushed to his breaking point. In preparation for the engagement party, Brayan tasks Ingrid with buying a gift for his fiancée.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: At the party, Andrés finds it painful to see the home that was once his, while Fernanda summons Brayan outside to talk. Leonidas meets with Florence.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Brayan is spotted in the parked car with Fernanda. Meanwhile, Liseth is seen with Mateo. Leonidas tries to make his escape from Florence.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: Fidel gets love advice from Leonidas. A drunken Ingrid seeks comfort from Miller. Andrés plots his revenge against Brayan for shaming him at the party.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: Andrés sets out to steal Brayan's fiancée. Fernanda tries every trick in the book to get Brayan to sleep with her. Fidel confronts Mateo about Liseth.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: Andrés makes a bold move toward Rosmery. Julio sets a plan in motion to get Andrés fired. Antonia learns the truth about Florence's financial situation.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Hugo tries to tip off Leonidas about Florence. Mateo learns some juicy gossip from Liseth. Rosmery investigates the allegations made against Andrés.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery finds the evidence she was looking for. Florence emotionally blackmails Leonidas. Ingrid makes another confession to Miller.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Andrés and Rosmery's rooftop chat ends in a mishap. Antonia finds something suspicious on Brayan's bed. Miller plays hardball with Ingrid.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: During a delivery, Fidel gets a gift. Andrés makes a confession to Leonidas. An overheard conversation gives Hugo a clue in solving the earring mystery.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Brayan scrambles to throw together a birthday celebration for Rosmery. Fernanda tries a different tack with Brayan. Liseth receives an anonymous letter.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: Antonia learns who the earring belongs to and confronts the owner. Leonidas sets out to win his bet with Orlando. Jealousy gets the better of Brayan.
episodes.title: Episode 36

episodes.synopsis: Leonidas asks Antonia to go on a date. Brayan chases after Fernanda, leaving Rosmery with Andrés at the party. Ingrid issues her own threat to Miller.
episodes.title: Episode 37

episodes.synopsis: Andrés accompanies Rosmery to Fernanda's apartment to see if Brayan is there, but when they arrive, Andrés tries to dissuade Rosmery from her mission.
episodes.title: Episode 38

episodes.synopsis: The next day, Antonia confronts Brayan over his infidelity. Andrés decides to put Rosmery's happiness ahead of his own. Liseth snoops in Mateo's office.
episodes.title: Episode 39

episodes.synopsis: Orlando makes a confession to Leonidas. Fernanda pressures Brayan to fire Rosmery, and while visiting his workplace, hears the name "Liseth."
episodes.title: Episode 40

episodes.synopsis: Fernanada tries to get Liseth to open up about her love life. Rosmery learns Liseth has a secret boyfriend. Brayan and Andrés play golf with Stein.
episodes.title: Episode 41

episodes.synopsis: Andrés tries to salvage the meeting with Stein. Fidel becomes Express World's go-to expert on writing love poems. Mateo treats Liseth cruelly.
episodes.title: Episode 42

episodes.synopsis: After learning his competition took Stein to a nightclub to seal the deal, Brayan devises a plan. Leonidas takes Antonia out for a night on the town.
episodes.title: Episode 43

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid finally gives Miller a try. When Stein names jobs cuts as a condition of the contract, Andrés shows him the impact that would have on the locals.
episodes.title: Episode 44

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery confides in Ingrid about her changing feelings for Andrés. Meanwhile, Andrés tries to work up the courage to ask out Rosmery.
episodes.title: Episode 45

episodes.synopsis: Stein names the winner of the contract. Liseth decides she needs a new man in order to get over Mateo. Antonia overhears Leonidas arguing with Orlando.
episodes.title: Episode 46

episodes.synopsis: Andrés learns what his new job duties will entail. Fernanda brings up the subject of marriage with Brayan. Julio offers Fidel a business deal.
episodes.title: Episode 47

episodes.synopsis: An emergency causes Andrés and Rosmery's outing to take a sudden, emotional turn. Miller and Liseth go on a date. Fernanda aims to move in with Brayan.
episodes.title: Episode 48

episodes.synopsis: Maritza orders Rosmery to stay away from her man. Andrés investigates Rosmery's parents' pension. Antonia confronts Orlando about his part in the bet.
episodes.title: Episode 49

episodes.synopsis: At work, Andrés teaches his first exercise class, and advises the Peláezes on investing the pension money. Hugo gets his hands on Fernanda's cellphone.
episodes.title: Episode 50

episodes.synopsis: As Liseth heads out to meet her date, Fidel follows her to see who it is. Rosmery and Ingrid return home to find their belongings on the sidewalk.
episodes.title: Episode 51

episodes.synopsis: At the concert, Andrés tries out his new dance skills with Rosmery, while Fidel spots Liseth — and her date — in the crowded venue.
episodes.title: Episode 52

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda catches Hugo surveilling her movements. Rosmery asks Andrés if they can just be friends. Antonia learns Fernanda spent the night with Mateo.
episodes.title: Episode 53

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda tells Brayan his fear of marriage leaves her no choice but to accept the Dubai job offer. Andrés and Rosmery begin work on their new business.
episodes.title: Episode 54

episodes.synopsis: Buyers of Fidel's love poems begin to complain. Miller gets a call about a possible job. Mr. Afanador has a candid chat with Liseth about his son.
episodes.title: Episode 55

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid learns Brayan is considering marriage to Fernanda. To show Brayan what he's giving up, Fernanda makes their last night together unforgettable.
episodes.title: Episode 56

episodes.synopsis: At the airport, Fernanda makes her goodbye to Brayan as heartbreaking as possible. Edmundo visits Leonidas. Andrés and Rosmery register their business.
episodes.title: Episode 57

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid asks to speak to Brayan alone. Antonia puts Fernanda's love for Brayan to the test. Andrés tries to talk to Maritza about a delicate matter.
episodes.title: Episode 58

episodes.synopsis: Brayan decides whether to accept Fernanda's terms. Andrés spends the evening dodging Maritza's advances. Rosmery witnesses something shocking.
episodes.title: Episode 59

episodes.synopsis: Leonidas crashes Brayan's marriage ceremony. Ingrid gets unwelcome news. While waiting to board his flight with Rosmery, Andrés runs into an old friend.
episodes.title: Episode 60

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery asks Andrés about Paulina. Maritza catches Ingrid doing something in secret in the bathroom. Brayan experiences his first airplane flight.
episodes.title: Episode 61

episodes.synopsis: Paulina visits Antonia. Andrés discovers the hotel he booked isn't what he expected. Mateo tells Fernanda what her next strategy with Brayan should be.
episodes.title: Episode 62

episodes.synopsis: Fidel discovers Ingrid is being blackmailed and demands she tell him why. Andrés finds it both difficult and wonderful to share a bed with Rosmery.
episodes.title: Episode 63

episodes.synopsis: Leonidas dictates a love poem for Miller to write down and give to Liseth. Fernanda recruits someone to help her achieve her goal with Brayan.
episodes.title: Episode 64

episodes.synopsis: Andrés finally gets Rosmery to reveal what has been bothering her. Liseth overhears a co-worker and his girlfriend talking about love poems he wrote.
episodes.title: Episode 65

episodes.synopsis: Fidel learns how Miller wooed Liseth. Fernanda readies Brayan to succumb to Estela's charms. At the hotel, Andrés gets a phone call from Paulina.
episodes.title: Episode 66

episodes.synopsis: Mateo and Julio scramble to cover their tracks and frame Fidel. Andrés receives another offer from the moped dealer. Liseth confronts Miller.
episodes.title: Episode 67

episodes.synopsis: The detective interrogates Fidel. Mateo and Julio make a statement to the police. Ingrid reveals to her siblings who the father of her unborn child is.
episodes.title: Episode 68

episodes.synopsis: Tax auditors arrive at Express World. Rosmery summons Miller to the hostel to discuss two important matters. Mateo learns of Andrés' moped order.
episodes.title: Episode 69

episodes.synopsis: Paulina invites Andrés to dinner and makes him a tempting offer. Edmundo's thugs finally corner Leonidas. Miller asks Brayan for a favor.
episodes.title: Episode 70

episodes.synopsis: Mateo comes home to an unpleasant surprise. After hearing Miller's news, Brayan explodes. Fernanda frames one of Antonia's maids for a theft.
episodes.title: Episode 71

episodes.synopsis: Antonia visits Express World and learns how bad its financial situation is. Liseth visits Fidel in jail. Fernanda introduces Brayan to the new maid.
episodes.title: Episode 72

episodes.synopsis: Andrés discovers Leonidas is missing and realizes something is very wrong. Nuri serves Brayan a beverage containing a secret ingredient.
episodes.title: Episode 73

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda gives Nuri further instructions in seducing Brayan. Rosmery overhears Paulina talking to Andrés about an offer she extended to him.
episodes.title: Episode 74

episodes.synopsis: Hugo overhears Nuri talking on the phone to Fernanda about retrieving the video cassette. Andrés sets in motion a plan to catch Edmundo red-handed.
episodes.title: Episode 75

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery intervenes in order to save Andrés' life. Following Fernanda's car, Brayan sees her pick up a male passenger. Miller proposes an idea to Ingrid.
episodes.title: Episode 76

episodes.synopsis: Brayan demands to know who Fernanda was with. Rosmery is unable to contain her jealousy toward Paulina. Andrés tries to find a buyer for the mopeds.
episodes.title: Episode 77

episodes.synopsis: Leonidas makes amends with Antonia. Brayan seeks birthday attention. Fidel asks Ingrid about her wedding preparations, and gets news from his lawyer.
episodes.title: Episode 78

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery gives Andrés a birthday celebration filled with lots of love. Brayan realizes the value of the old life he gave up and visits the hostel.
episodes.title: Episode 79

episodes.synopsis: Andrés discovers his moped shipment is missing. Rosmery asks Paulina a blunt question. Brayan informs his wife that they're moving to a new home.
episodes.title: Episode 80

episodes.synopsis: Antonia learns of Andrés' financial troubles and tries to help. Ingrid breaks the bad news to Fidel. Brayan takes his wife shopping at the local mall.
episodes.title: Episode 81

episodes.synopsis: When the neighborhood investors demand Andrés return their money, Brayan offers a solution. Fernanda comes up with a new strategy to use on Brayan.
episodes.title: Episode 82

episodes.synopsis: Andrés starts his new job. Fidel's bail is finally paid. Pushed to the limit of what she can tolerate, Fernanda recruits Maritza to help frame Brayan.
episodes.title: Episode 83

episodes.synopsis: Andrés and Leonidas move to a new home. Fernanda returns to her apartment, where a shocking scene awaits. Liseth calls Fidel in hopes of reconciling.
episodes.title: Episode 84

episodes.synopsis: Paulina takes Andrés to dinner to celebrate his first day on the job. Fidel forces Miller to name who's behind the smuggling — and to do one more thing.
episodes.title: Episode 85

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid and Miller visit the doctor for a prenatal ultrasound. Andrés attends a work meeting on the golf course. Leonidas takes Antonia on an outing.
episodes.title: Episode 86

episodes.synopsis: Mateo urges Brayan to postpone his divorce plans. Rosmery tries to reach Andrés but Paulina thwarts her efforts. Leonidas makes a confession to Antonia.
episodes.title: Episode 87

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery sees Paulina leaving Andrés' apartment building and confronts her. Maritza spots a prime photo opportunity and captures the moment.
episodes.title: Episode 88

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid's attack on Fernanda has unexpected consequences. Andrés looks for Rosmery at the hostel, where Maritza gives him news he doesn't quite believe.
episodes.title: Episode 89

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid's experience leaves her profoundly changed. When Fernanda forbids Andrés from deleting the photo on her phone, he becomes suspicious.
episodes.title: Episode 90

episodes.synopsis: Liseth visits Fidel in person to ask for a second chance. Andrés turns to Paulina for company while drowning his sorrows in booze.
episodes.title: Episode 91

episodes.synopsis: Brayan meets his divorce lawyer. Facing eviction, Fidel reconsiders Edmundo's offer. A co-worker urges Andrés to use the photo to ruin Express World.
episodes.title: Episode 92

episodes.synopsis: Carlos makes Fernanda an offer. Maritza gives Ingrid a makeover. Stein from Redex visits Express World and is surprised to learn Andrés isn't there.
episodes.title: Episode 93

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda tries to take over Antonia's home. Tough Cookie teaches Fidel to let a gun do the talking. Maritza takes the transformed Ingrid out dancing.
episodes.title: Episode 94

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid's new look leaves a strong impression on Miller — and Brayan. Liseth shares with Andrés some suspicions she has about Mateo.
episodes.title: Episode 95

episodes.synopsis: The photo of Brayan and Rosmery appears on the covers of all the tabloids. Without her eyeglasses, Ingrid runs into danger — and a possible career.
episodes.title: Episode 96

episodes.synopsis: Antonia visits Maritza to negotiate a solution to Brayan's impending divorce. Ingrid takes Harold up on his offer and attends her first photo shoot.
episodes.title: Episode 97

episodes.synopsis: Rosmery and Liseth try to find out how Mateo is connected to Héctor. Mateo sees only one option left that will give Brayan's fortune to Fernanda.
episodes.title: Episode 98

episodes.synopsis: Andrés asks Rosmery about the night Maritza took the photo. At the party, Ingrid tries to avoid being seen by Brayan, and Fernanda uses the poison.
episodes.title: Episode 99

episodes.synopsis: Brayan finds a way to bring the party to a swift end, but unintended consequences also result. Andrés realizes he must make some changes in his life.
episodes.title: Episode 100

episodes.synopsis: Paulina makes a confession to Andrés. Mateo tells Julio he has a special job for him. Fidel's association with Edmundo puts him in danger.
episodes.title: Episode 101

episodes.synopsis: With Harold's help, Ingrid creates a portfolio and shows Camilo. Maritza toughens up Fidel's image. Antonia and Leonidas tell their sons they're dating.
episodes.title: Episode 102

episodes.synopsis: Andrés gets a phone call from the moped dealer. Tough Cookie goes to the hostel to abduct Maritza. Miller catches Ingrid admiring her new passport.
episodes.title: Episode 103

episodes.synopsis: Andrés remembers where he's seen Héctor before. Mateo takes steps to deflect blame for the theft of the mopeds. Miller follows Ingrid and spies on her.
episodes.title: Episode 104

episodes.synopsis: Edmundo asks Fidel to fulfill a revenge mission. At the club, jealousy gets the better of Miller. Rosmery tries to charm the truth out of Héctor.
episodes.title: Episode 105

episodes.synopsis: Hugo wrestles with confusing feelings for Antonia. Rosmery learns Ingrid hasn't been going to school. Maritza corners Fidel at his new workplace.
episodes.title: Episode 106

episodes.synopsis: Andrés is ambushed. When Brayan makes plans to drive his SUV instead of his convertible, Fernanda must act fast. Maritza makes a confession to Fidel.
episodes.title: Episode 107

episodes.synopsis: Camilo gives Ingrid a pep talk. Brayan's lawyer visits Express World to deliver the news of the court's ruling. Fidel tells Edmundo he wants to quit.
episodes.title: Episode 108

episodes.synopsis: When Antonia is forced out of her home, the stress is too much for her to bear. Ingrid learns Brayan is missing. Liseth makes a horrifying discovery.
episodes.title: Episode 109

episodes.synopsis: A dazed Brayan runs into trouble. The doctor gives an update on Antonia's condition. Tough Cookie returns to the hostel to finish the job on Andrés.
episodes.title: Episode 110

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda has her first day as co-owner of Express World. Edmundo prepares to escape from jail. Antonia awakens and asks Andrés to do something for her.
episodes.title: Episode 111

episodes.synopsis: Just as Fernanda begins firing Express World staff, Andrés shows up. Hugo finds a clue near the crash site. Ingrid receives a warning from a co-worker.
episodes.title: Episode 112

episodes.synopsis: Fidel and his crew intercept the inmate transport truck. Fernanda and Mateo meet with Carlos to negotiate his purchase of her half of Express World.
episodes.title: Episode 113

episodes.synopsis: Dussan takes Brayan to the country club. The police come looking for Fidel. Ingrid and Detective Marrón visit the jail to see if Brayan was there.
episodes.title: Episode 114

episodes.synopsis: After Florence tells Brayan where the Ferreira estate is, he and Dussan go there. When Fidel asks for his old job back, Liseth becomes suspicious.
episodes.title: Episode 115

episodes.synopsis: Hugo reveals to Leonidas a big decision he's made. Fidel prepares for his delivery to Ecuador. Julio and Mateo take steps to collect the reward money.
episodes.title: Episode 116

episodes.synopsis: Mateo goes to pick up the reward money. An accidental stowaway goes along for the ride to Ecuador. Mr. Afanador arrives at his ex-wife's home.
episodes.title: Episode 117

episodes.synopsis: Fidel discovers the stowaway in the back of the truck. Mateo bumps into a mysterious woman. Ingrid finally admits to Rosmery her feelings for Brayan.
episodes.title: Episode 118

episodes.synopsis: Encouraged by Liseth, Fidel stands up to Edmundo. Ingrid continues her hospital search for Brayan. Mateo gets a call on the mystery woman's phone.
episodes.title: Episode 119

episodes.synopsis: When Carlos meets with Mateo to pay for the Express World shares, someone eavesdrops. Miller's parents find their son. Brayan gets a medical prognosis.
episodes.title: Episode 120

episodes.synopsis: Brayan's loved ones fill him in on his complex past. Maritza sees Fidel and Liseth embracing and becomes unhinged. Mateo and Fabia go out on a date.
episodes.title: Episode 121

episodes.synopsis: Maritza finds a possible way to get Fidel to marry her. Fernanda surprises Mateo at his office — while Fabia is there. Hugo begins a revenge mission.
episodes.title: Episode 122

episodes.synopsis: Miller learns what his options are. Brayan insists on attending Express World's first board meeting with Carlos. Fabia gives Mateo an ultimatum.
episodes.title: Episode 123

episodes.synopsis: At the hostel, Brayan tries to see if he can remember anything about living there with Leonidas. Maritza presents Fidel with her secret weapon.
episodes.title: Episode 124

episodes.synopsis: Brayan starts to remember the events that preceded his car crash. Miller receives his sentence. Ingrid investigates to see if Maritza's claim is true.
episodes.title: Episode 125

episodes.synopsis: Fabia expresses financial concerns to Mateo. Julio is shocked to see Dussan at Express World. Detective Barrón brings Brayan to the crash site.
episodes.title: Episode 126

episodes.synopsis: Ingrid drags Maritza to a clinic for a prenatal check. Andrés hunts for the phone that was on Julio's desk. Brayan makes an accusation against Andrés.
episodes.title: Episode 127

episodes.synopsis: Mateo tries to convince Fernanda to postpone their departure to the Bahamas. Miller has a rough first night with his new cellmate.
episodes.title: Episode 128

episodes.synopsis: Mateo and Fernanda head to the airport to make their escape. Rosmery sneaks into the Ferreira estate. Miller gets in trouble over a bread roll.
episodes.title: Episode 129

episodes.synopsis: Mateo dodges airport security but Fernanda isn't so lucky. Ingrid surprises Maritza with an ultrasound appointment. Fabia delivers the cash to her boss.
episodes.title: Episode 130

episodes.synopsis: Miller receives a visit from his dad. Mateo is forced to stay with Héctor and his mom. Ingrid, Fidel, Liseth and Maritza watch the ultrasound recording.
episodes.title: Episode 131

episodes.synopsis: Hugo finds out some info about Fabia. Miller accidentally overhears Peluche making plans. Andrés and Julio are told they're being transferred.
episodes.title: Episode 132

episodes.synopsis: Andrés and Julio arrive at their new home. Maritza makes the final arrangements for her wedding. At the country club, Fernanda spots two familiar faces.
episodes.title: Episode 133

episodes.synopsis: Fernanda helps Mateo, but not because she's forgiven him. One of Andres' loved ones sneaks into the prison. Carlos pressures Brayan to switch insurers.
episodes.title: Episode 134

episodes.synopsis: Lonely Brayan has a vivid dream. Ingrid double-checks something on the ultrasound video. Fernanda makes Mateo earn his keep. Maritza's big day arrives.
episodes.title: Episode 135

episodes.synopsis: Hugo gets a tip that Fabia is at the airport. Andrés sees Héctor visiting Julio and asks his dad to follow him. At the wedding, Rosmery stalls for time.
episodes.title: Episode 136

episodes.synopsis: Brayan has a heart-to-heart with Ingrid. Fernanda spots Fabia at the country club and goes after her. Miller asks to join Peluche's escape plan.
episodes.title: Episode 137

episodes.synopsis: At the country club, Fernanda eavesdrops on a meeting between Carlos and former whiskey smuggler Erminson. Fabia leverages Héctor's weakness for women.
episodes.title: Episode 138

episodes.synopsis: Mateo must wear a disguise in order to pay a "conjugal visit" to Julio. Elsewhere in the prison, Rosmery, Antonia and Ingrid visit Andrés and Miller.
episodes.title: Episode 139

episodes.synopsis: Maritza offers a proposal to Mr. Afanador. At the country club, Antonia confronts Judge Yacamán. Ingrid visits ex-boyfriend Camilo to make a request.
episodes.title: Episode 140

episodes.synopsis: Andrés tries to talk Miller out of escaping. Camilo begs Ingrid for a second chance. Mr. Afanador's ex-wife pays a surprise visit and meets Maritza.
episodes.title: Episode 141

episodes.synopsis: Genoveva tells her ex-husband the reason for her sudden visit. Julio finds out Andrés saved him after he passed out. Brayan gets an alarming phone call.
episodes.title: Episode 142

episodes.synopsis: When Julio loses all faith in Mateo, Andrés offers him help. Antonia delegates jobs to manage Express World's crisis. Ingrid gives Camilo her decision.
episodes.title: Episode 143

episodes.synopsis: Maritza cooks up a love potion to give to Mr. Afanador. Fernanda comes to a realization about Mateo. Julio testifies before Judge Yacamán.
episodes.title: Episode 144

episodes.synopsis: Camilo shares big news with Ingrid. Miller is granted bail, but paying it might require a sacrifice. Andres' release from prison comes with a surprise.
episodes.title: Episode 145

episodes.synopsis: After Carlos returns the money, Mateo and Trujillo launch their plan against Fernanda. Brayan admits his many regrets to Andrés, who proposes an idea.
episodes.title: Episode 146

episodes.synopsis: Mateo goes to stay with Nuri, but discovers he's been followed. Ingrid decides about Madrid. An incoming call gives Fernanda a chance to be rescued.
episodes.title: Episode 147
